{"doc":{"isMarkdown":false,"isTranslated":true,"isActive":true,"flaws":{},"title":"Categorias de conteúdo","mdn_url":"/pt-BR/docs/Web/Guide/HTML/Content_categories","locale":"pt-BR","native":"Português (do Brasil)","sidebarHTML":"","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<p><span class=\"seoSummary\">Cada elemento HTML deve permanecer, por regras, definindo que tipo de conteúdo ele pode ter. Essas regras estão agrupadas em modelos de conteúdo para muitos elementos. Cada elemento HTML pertence a nenhum, um, ou múltiplos modelos de conteúdo, cada regra de definição&nbsp;que o conteúdo do elemento deve seguir em um documento HTML.</span></p>\n\n<p>Há três tipos de categorias de conteúdo:</p>\n\n<ul>\n <li>Principais categorias de conteúdo, as quais descrevem regras comuns de conteúdo compartilhado por vários elementos;</li>\n <li>Categorias de conteúdo relacionado, as quais decrevem regras comuns de conteúdo para elementos&nbsp;relacioados;</li>\n <li>Categorias de conteúdo específico, as quais descrevem categorias raras compartilhadas somente por poucos elementos, às vezes apenas em um contexto específico.</li>\n</ul>\n\n<div style=\"width: 50%;\" id=\"sect1\"><a href=\"/@api/deki/files/6244/=Content_categories_venn.png\" title=\"This is a link to an unwritten page\" class=\"page-not-created\"><img alt=\"Content_categories_venn.png\" class=\"default internal\" src=\"/@api/deki/files/6244/=Content_categories_venn.png?size=webview\" loading=\"lazy\"></a></div>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"principais_categorias_de_conteúdo","title":"Principais categorias de conteúdo","isH3":false,"content":""}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"conteúdo_de_metadados","title":"Conteúdo de metadados","isH3":true,"content":"<p>Os elementos pertencentes a categoria&nbsp;<em>conteúdo de metadados&nbsp;</em>modificam a apresentação ou o comportamento do resto do documento, define ligações para outros documentos ou transmite outras informações&nbsp;<em>fora da banda.</em></p>\n\n<p>Os elementos pertencentes a essa categoria são <a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/HTML/Element/base\"><code>&lt;base&gt;</code></a>, <a class=\"page-not-created\" title=\"A documentação sobre isto ainda não foi escrita; por favor considere contribuir!\"><code>&lt;command&gt;</code></a>, <a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/HTML/Element/link\"><code>&lt;link&gt;</code></a>, <a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/HTML/Element/meta\"><code>&lt;meta&gt;</code></a>, <a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/HTML/Element/noscript\"><code>&lt;noscript&gt;</code></a>, <a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/HTML/Element/script\"><code>&lt;script&gt;</code></a>, <a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/HTML/Element/style\"><code>&lt;style&gt;</code></a> e&nbsp;<a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/HTML/Element/title\"><code>&lt;title&gt;</code></a>.</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"conteúdo_de_fluxo","title":"<a name=\"flow_content\">Conteúdo de fluxo</a>","isH3":true,"content":"<p>Elementos pertencentes a categoria de conteúdo de fluxo tipicamente contém texto ou conteúdo embutido. Eles são: <a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/HTML/Element/a\"><code>&lt;a&gt;</code></a>, <a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/HTML/Element/abbr\"><code>&lt;abbr&gt;</code></a>, <a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/HTML/Element/address\"><code>&lt;address&gt;</code></a>, <a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/HTML/Element/article\"><code>&lt;article&gt;</code></a>, <a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/HTML/Element/aside\"><code>&lt;aside&gt;</code></a>, <a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/HTML/Element/Audio\"><code>&lt;audio&gt;</code></a>, <a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/HTML/Element/b\"><code>&lt;b&gt;</code></a>,<a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/HTML/Element/bdo\"><code>&lt;bdo&gt;</code></a>, <a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/HTML/Element/bdi\"><code>&lt;bdi&gt;</code></a>, <a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/HTML/Element/blockquote\"><code>&lt;blockquote&gt;</code></a>, <a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/HTML/Element/br\"><code>&lt;br&gt;</code></a>, <a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/HTML/Element/button\"><code>&lt;button&gt;</code></a>, <a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/HTML/Element/canvas\"><code>&lt;canvas&gt;</code></a>, <a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/HTML/Element/cite\"><code>&lt;cite&gt;</code></a>, <a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/HTML/Element/code\"><code>&lt;code&gt;</code></a>, <a class=\"page-not-created\" title=\"A documentação sobre isto ainda não foi escrita; por favor considere contribuir!\"><code>&lt;command&gt;</code></a>, <a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/HTML/Element/data\"><code>&lt;data&gt;</code></a>, <a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/HTML/Element/datalist\"><code>&lt;datalist&gt;</code></a>, <a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/HTML/Element/del\"><code>&lt;del&gt;</code></a>, <a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/HTML/Element/details\"><code>&lt;details&gt;</code></a>, <a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/HTML/Element/dfn\"><code>&lt;dfn&gt;</code></a>, <a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/HTML/Element/div\"><code>&lt;div&gt;</code></a>, <a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/HTML/Element/dl\"><code>&lt;dl&gt;</code></a>, <a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/HTML/Element/em\"><code>&lt;em&gt;</code></a>, <a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/HTML/Element/embed\"><code>&lt;embed&gt;</code></a>, <a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/HTML/Element/fieldset\"><code>&lt;fieldset&gt;</code></a>, <a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/HTML/Element/figure\"><code>&lt;figure&gt;</code></a>, <a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/HTML/Element/footer\"><code>&lt;footer&gt;</code></a>, <a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/HTML/Element/form\"><code>&lt;form&gt;</code></a>, <a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/Heading_Elements\"><code>&lt;h1&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a>, <a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/Heading_Elements\"><code>&lt;h2&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a>, <a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/Heading_Elements\"><code>&lt;h3&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a>, <a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/Heading_Elements\"><code>&lt;h4&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a>, <a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/Heading_Elements\"><code>&lt;h5&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a>, <a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/Heading_Elements\"><code>&lt;h6&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a>, <a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/HTML/Element/header\"><code>&lt;header&gt;</code></a>, <a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/HTML/Element/hgroup\"><code>&lt;hgroup&gt;</code></a>, <a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/HTML/Element/hr\"><code>&lt;hr&gt;</code></a>, <a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/HTML/Element/i\"><code>&lt;i&gt;</code></a>, <a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/HTML/Element/iframe\"><code>&lt;iframe&gt;</code></a>, <a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/HTML/Element/img\"><code>&lt;img&gt;</code></a>, <a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/HTML/Element/Input\"><code>&lt;input&gt;</code></a>, <a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/HTML/Element/ins\"><code>&lt;ins&gt;</code></a>, <a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/kbd\"><code>&lt;kbd&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a>, <a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/keygen\"><code>&lt;keygen&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a>, <a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/HTML/Element/label\"><code>&lt;label&gt;</code></a>, <a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/HTML/Element/main\"><code>&lt;main&gt;</code></a>, <a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/HTML/Element/map\"><code>&lt;map&gt;</code></a>, <a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/HTML/Element/mark\"><code>&lt;mark&gt;</code></a>, <code><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/MathML/Element/math\" title=\"<math>\">&lt;math&gt;</a></code>, <a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/menu\"><code>&lt;menu&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a>, <a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/HTML/Element/meter\"><code>&lt;meter&gt;</code></a>, <a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/HTML/Element/nav\"><code>&lt;nav&gt;</code></a>, <a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/HTML/Element/noscript\"><code>&lt;noscript&gt;</code></a>, <a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/object\"><code>&lt;object&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a>, <a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/HTML/Element/ol\"><code>&lt;ol&gt;</code></a>, <a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/HTML/Element/Output\"><code>&lt;output&gt;</code></a>, <a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/HTML/Element/p\"><code>&lt;p&gt;</code></a>, <a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/HTML/Element/pre\"><code>&lt;pre&gt;</code></a>, <a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/HTML/Element/progress\"><code>&lt;progress&gt;</code></a>, <a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/HTML/Element/q\"><code>&lt;q&gt;</code></a>, <a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/HTML/Element/ruby\"><code>&lt;ruby&gt;</code></a>, <a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/HTML/Element/s\"><code>&lt;s&gt;</code></a>, <a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/samp\"><code>&lt;samp&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a>, <a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/HTML/Element/script\"><code>&lt;script&gt;</code></a>, <a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/HTML/Element/section\"><code>&lt;section&gt;</code></a>, <a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/HTML/Element/select\"><code>&lt;select&gt;</code></a>, <a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/small\"><code>&lt;small&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a>, <a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/HTML/Element/span\"><code>&lt;span&gt;</code></a>, <a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/HTML/Element/strong\"><code>&lt;strong&gt;</code></a>, <a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/sub\"><code>&lt;sub&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a>, <a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/sup\"><code>&lt;sup&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a>, <a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/SVG/Element/svg\"><code>&lt;svg&gt;</code></a>, <a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/HTML/Element/table\"><code>&lt;table&gt;</code></a>, <a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/HTML/Element/template\"><code>&lt;template&gt;</code></a>, <a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/HTML/Element/textarea\"><code>&lt;textarea&gt;</code></a>, <a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/HTML/Element/time\"><code>&lt;time&gt;</code></a>, <a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/HTML/Element/ul\"><code>&lt;ul&gt;</code></a>, <a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/HTML/Element/var\"><code>&lt;var&gt;</code></a>, <a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/HTML/Element/Video\"><code>&lt;video&gt;</code></a>, <a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/HTML/Element/wbr\"><code>&lt;wbr&gt;</code></a> e&nbsp;Text.</p>\n\n<p>Alguns outros elementos pertencem a essa categoria, mas somente se uma condição específica é realizada:</p>\n\n<ul>\n <li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/HTML/Element/area\"><code>&lt;area&gt;</code></a>, se for&nbsp;um descendente de um elemento&nbsp;<a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/HTML/Element/map\"><code>&lt;map&gt;</code></a></li>\n <li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/HTML/Element/link\"><code>&lt;link&gt;</code></a>, se o atributo&nbsp;<strong><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Global_attributes#attr-itemprop\" title=\"HTML/Global attributes#itemprop\">itemprop</a>&nbsp;</strong>estiver&nbsp;presente</li>\n <li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/HTML/Element/meta\"><code>&lt;meta&gt;</code></a>, se o atributo&nbsp;<a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Global_attributes#attr-itemprop\" title=\"HTML/Global attributes#itemprop\"><strong>itemprop</strong></a> estiver&nbsp;presente</li>\n <li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/HTML/Element/style\"><code>&lt;style&gt;</code></a>, se o atributo&nbsp;<a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/HTML/Element/style#attr-scoped\"><code>scoped</code></a> estiver presente</li>\n</ul>","titleAsText":"Conteúdo de fluxo"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"conteúdo_de_seccionamento","title":"Conteúdo de seccionamento","isH3":true,"content":"<p>Os elementos pertencentes ao modelo de conteúdo de seccionamento criam uma&nbsp;<a href=\"/en-US/docs/Sections_and_Outlines_of_an_HTML5_document\" title=\"This is a link to an unwritten page\" class=\"page-not-created\">seção no esboço atual</a>&nbsp;que define o escopo&nbsp;dos elementos <a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/HTML/Element/header\"><code>&lt;header&gt;</code></a>, elementos <a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/HTML/Element/footer\"><code>&lt;footer&gt;</code></a> e&nbsp;na&nbsp;<a href=\"#heading_content\" title=\"#heading content\">conteúdo do cabeçalho</a>.</p>\n\n<p>Elementos pertencentes a essa categoria são&nbsp;<a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/HTML/Element/article\"><code>&lt;article&gt;</code></a>, <a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/HTML/Element/aside\"><code>&lt;aside&gt;</code></a>, <a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/HTML/Element/nav\"><code>&lt;nav&gt;</code></a> e&nbsp;<a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/HTML/Element/section\"><code>&lt;section&gt;</code></a>.&nbsp;</p>\n\n<div class=\"note notecard\" id=\"sect2\">\n<p><em>Nota:</em>&nbsp;Não confunda esse modelo de conteúdo com a categoria de&nbsp;<a href=\"/en-US/docs/Sections_and_Outlines_of_an_HTML5_document#sectioning_root\" title=\"This is a link to an unwritten page\" class=\"page-not-created\">seccionamento raiz</a>&nbsp;que isola seus conteúdos dos esboços regulares.</p>\n</div>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"conteúdo_do_cabeçalho","title":"Conteúdo do cabeçalho","isH3":true,"content":"<p>O conteúdo do cabeçalho define o título de uma seção, se é marcada por&nbsp;um explícito elemento do&nbsp;<a href=\"#sectioning_content\" title=\"#sectioning content\">conteúdo de seccionamento</a>&nbsp;ou&nbsp;implicitamente definido pelo próprio conteúdo do cabeçalho.</p>\n\n<p>Os elementos pertencentes a essa categoria são&nbsp;<a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/Heading_Elements\"><code>&lt;h1&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a>, <a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/Heading_Elements\"><code>&lt;h2&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a>, <a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/Heading_Elements\"><code>&lt;h3&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a>, <a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/Heading_Elements\"><code>&lt;h4&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a>, <a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/Heading_Elements\"><code>&lt;h5&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a>, <a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/Heading_Elements\"><code>&lt;h6&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a> e&nbsp;<a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/HTML/Element/hgroup\"><code>&lt;hgroup&gt;</code></a>.</p>\n\n<div class=\"note notecard\" id=\"sect3\">\n<p><em>Note:</em>&nbsp;Embora provavelmente contenha algum conteúdo do cabeçalho, o&nbsp;<a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/HTML/Element/header\"><code>&lt;header&gt;</code></a> não faz parte do conteúdo do cabeçalho em si.</p>\n</div>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"conteúdo_fraseado","title":"Conteúdo fraseado","isH3":true,"content":"<p>O conteúdo fraseado&nbsp;define o texto e a marcação que ele contém. Séries de conteúdos fraseados compõem parágrafos.</p>\n\n<p>Os elementos pertencentes a essa categoria são <a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/HTML/Element/abbr\"><code>&lt;abbr&gt;</code></a>, <a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/HTML/Element/Audio\"><code>&lt;audio&gt;</code></a>, <a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/HTML/Element/b\"><code>&lt;b&gt;</code></a>, <a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/HTML/Element/bdo\"><code>&lt;bdo&gt;</code></a>, <a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/HTML/Element/br\"><code>&lt;br&gt;</code></a>, <a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/HTML/Element/button\"><code>&lt;button&gt;</code></a>, <a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/HTML/Element/canvas\"><code>&lt;canvas&gt;</code></a>, <a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/HTML/Element/cite\"><code>&lt;cite&gt;</code></a>, <a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/HTML/Element/code\"><code>&lt;code&gt;</code></a>, <a class=\"page-not-created\" title=\"A documentação sobre isto ainda não foi escrita; por favor considere contribuir!\"><code>&lt;command&gt;</code></a>, <a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/HTML/Element/datalist\"><code>&lt;datalist&gt;</code></a>, <a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/HTML/Element/dfn\"><code>&lt;dfn&gt;</code></a>, <a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/HTML/Element/em\"><code>&lt;em&gt;</code></a>, <a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/HTML/Element/embed\"><code>&lt;embed&gt;</code></a>, <a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/HTML/Element/i\"><code>&lt;i&gt;</code></a>, <a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/HTML/Element/iframe\"><code>&lt;iframe&gt;</code></a>, <a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/HTML/Element/img\"><code>&lt;img&gt;</code></a>, <a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/HTML/Element/Input\"><code>&lt;input&gt;</code></a>, <a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/kbd\"><code>&lt;kbd&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a>, <a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/keygen\"><code>&lt;keygen&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a>, <a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/HTML/Element/label\"><code>&lt;label&gt;</code></a>, <a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/HTML/Element/mark\"><code>&lt;mark&gt;</code></a>, <code><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/MathML/Element/math\" title=\"<math>\">&lt;math&gt;</a></code>, <a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/HTML/Element/meter\"><code>&lt;meter&gt;</code></a>, <a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/HTML/Element/noscript\"><code>&lt;noscript&gt;</code></a>, <a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/object\"><code>&lt;object&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a>, <a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/HTML/Element/Output\"><code>&lt;output&gt;</code></a>, <a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/HTML/Element/progress\"><code>&lt;progress&gt;</code></a>, <a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/HTML/Element/q\"><code>&lt;q&gt;</code></a>, <a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/HTML/Element/ruby\"><code>&lt;ruby&gt;</code></a>, <a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/samp\"><code>&lt;samp&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a>, <a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/HTML/Element/script\"><code>&lt;script&gt;</code></a>, <a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/HTML/Element/select\"><code>&lt;select&gt;</code></a>, <a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/small\"><code>&lt;small&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a>, <a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/HTML/Element/span\"><code>&lt;span&gt;</code></a>, <a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/HTML/Element/strong\"><code>&lt;strong&gt;</code></a>, <a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/sub\"><code>&lt;sub&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a>, <a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/sup\"><code>&lt;sup&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a>, <a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/SVG/Element/svg\"><code>&lt;svg&gt;</code></a>, <a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/HTML/Element/textarea\"><code>&lt;textarea&gt;</code></a>, <a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/HTML/Element/time\"><code>&lt;time&gt;</code></a>, <a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/HTML/Element/var\"><code>&lt;var&gt;</code></a>, <a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/HTML/Element/Video\"><code>&lt;video&gt;</code></a>, <a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/HTML/Element/wbr\"><code>&lt;wbr&gt;</code></a> e texto simples (não consistindo somente de caracteres de espaço em branco).</p>\n\n<p>Alguns outros elementos pertencem a essa categoria, mas somente se uma condição específica é realizada:</p>\n\n<ul>\n <li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/HTML/Element/a\"><code>&lt;a&gt;</code></a>, se contém somente conteúdo fraseado</li>\n <li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/HTML/Element/area\"><code>&lt;area&gt;</code></a>, se for um descendente de um elemento <a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/HTML/Element/map\"><code>&lt;map&gt;</code></a></li>\n <li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/HTML/Element/del\"><code>&lt;del&gt;</code></a>, se contém somente conteúdo fraseado</li>\n <li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/HTML/Element/ins\"><code>&lt;ins&gt;</code></a>, se contém somente conteúdo fraseado</li>\n <li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/HTML/Element/link\"><code>&lt;link&gt;</code></a>, se o atributo&nbsp;<a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Global_attributes#attr-itemprop\" title=\"HTML/Global attributes#itemprop\"><strong>itemprop</strong></a> estiver&nbsp;presente</li>\n <li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/HTML/Element/map\"><code>&lt;map&gt;</code></a>, se contém somente conteúdo fraseado</li>\n <li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/HTML/Element/meta\"><code>&lt;meta&gt;</code></a>,&nbsp;se o atributo&nbsp;<a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Global_attributes#attr-itemprop\" title=\"HTML/Global attributes#itemprop\"><strong>itemprop</strong></a> estiver&nbsp;presente</li>\n</ul>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"conteúdo_embutido","title":"Conteúdo embutido","isH3":true,"content":"<p>O conteúdo embutido importa outro recurso ou&nbsp;insere conteúdo de uma outra linguagem de marcação&nbsp;no documento.&nbsp;Os elementos que pertencem a essa categoria incluem: <a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/HTML/Element/Audio\"><code>&lt;audio&gt;</code></a>, <a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/HTML/Element/canvas\"><code>&lt;canvas&gt;</code></a>, <a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/HTML/Element/embed\"><code>&lt;embed&gt;</code></a>, <a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/HTML/Element/iframe\"><code>&lt;iframe&gt;</code></a>, <a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/HTML/Element/img\"><code>&lt;img&gt;</code></a>, <code><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/MathML/Element/math\" title=\"<math>\">&lt;math&gt;</a></code>, <a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/object\"><code>&lt;object&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a>, <a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/SVG/Element/svg\"><code>&lt;svg&gt;</code></a> e&nbsp;<a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/HTML/Element/Video\"><code>&lt;video&gt;</code></a>.</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"conteúdo_interativo","title":"<a name=\"interactive_content\">Conteúdo interativo</a>","isH3":true,"content":"<p>O conteúdo interativo inclui elementos que são especificamente desenvolvidos para a interação do usuário. Os elementos que pertencem a essa categoria incluem:&nbsp;<a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/HTML/Element/a\"><code>&lt;a&gt;</code></a>, <a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/HTML/Element/button\"><code>&lt;button&gt;</code></a>, <a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/HTML/Element/details\"><code>&lt;details&gt;</code></a>, <a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/HTML/Element/embed\"><code>&lt;embed&gt;</code></a>, <a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/HTML/Element/iframe\"><code>&lt;iframe&gt;</code></a>, <a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/keygen\"><code>&lt;keygen&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a>, <a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/HTML/Element/label\"><code>&lt;label&gt;</code></a>, <a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/HTML/Element/select\"><code>&lt;select&gt;</code></a>, e&nbsp;<a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/HTML/Element/textarea\"><code>&lt;textarea&gt;</code></a>. Alguns elementos pertencem a essa categoria somente sob condições específicas:</p>\n\n<ul>\n <li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/HTML/Element/Audio\"><code>&lt;audio&gt;</code></a>, se o atributo&nbsp;<a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/HTML/Element/Audio#attr-controls\"><code>controls</code></a> estiver presente</li>\n <li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/HTML/Element/img\"><code>&lt;img&gt;</code></a>, se o atributo&nbsp;<a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/HTML/Element/img#attr-usemap\"><code>usemap</code></a> estiver presente</li>\n <li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/HTML/Element/Input\"><code>&lt;input&gt;</code></a>, se o atributo&nbsp;<a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/HTML/Element/Input#attr-type\"><code>type</code></a> não estiver no modo escondido</li>\n <li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/menu\"><code>&lt;menu&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a>, se o atributo&nbsp;<a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/menu\"><code>type</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a> estiver no modo barra de ferramentas</li>\n <li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/object\"><code>&lt;object&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a>, se o atributo&nbsp;<a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/object\"><code>usemap</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a> estiver presente</li>\n <li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/HTML/Element/Video\"><code>&lt;video&gt;</code></a>, se o atributo&nbsp;<a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/HTML/Element/Video#attr-controls\"><code>controls</code></a> estiver presente</li>\n</ul>","titleAsText":"Conteúdo interativo"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"conteúdo_associado_ao_form","title":"Conteúdo associado ao&nbsp;<strong>form</strong>","isH3":true,"content":"<p>O conteúdo associado ao&nbsp;<strong>form</strong>&nbsp;compreende elementos que têm um formulário de proprietário, exposto por um atributo&nbsp;<strong>form</strong>. Um&nbsp;formulário de proprietário é ou&nbsp;um elemento&nbsp;<a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/HTML/Element/form\"><code>&lt;form&gt;</code></a> ou o elemento o qual o ID é especificado no atributo&nbsp;<strong>form</strong>.</p>\n\n<ul>\n <li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/HTML/Element/button\"><code>&lt;button&gt;</code></a></li>\n <li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/HTML/Element/fieldset\"><code>&lt;fieldset&gt;</code></a></li>\n <li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/HTML/Element/Input\"><code>&lt;input&gt;</code></a></li>\n <li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/keygen\"><code>&lt;keygen&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li>\n <li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/HTML/Element/label\"><code>&lt;label&gt;</code></a></li>\n <li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/HTML/Element/meter\"><code>&lt;meter&gt;</code></a></li>\n <li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/object\"><code>&lt;object&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li>\n <li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/HTML/Element/Output\"><code>&lt;output&gt;</code></a></li>\n <li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/HTML/Element/progress\"><code>&lt;progress&gt;</code></a></li>\n <li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/HTML/Element/select\"><code>&lt;select&gt;</code></a></li>\n <li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/HTML/Element/textarea\"><code>&lt;textarea&gt;</code></a></li>\n</ul>\n\n<p>&nbsp;Essa categoria contém várias sub-categorias:</p>\n\n<dl>\n <dt id=\"listed\"><a name=\"Form_listed\">listed</a></dt>\n <dd>Elementos que estão listados nas coleções IDL&nbsp;<a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/HTMLFormElement/elements\" title=\"DOM/form.elements\">form.elements</a>&nbsp;e fieldset.elements. Contém&nbsp;<a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/HTML/Element/button\"><code>&lt;button&gt;</code></a>, <a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/HTML/Element/fieldset\"><code>&lt;fieldset&gt;</code></a>, <a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/HTML/Element/Input\"><code>&lt;input&gt;</code></a>, <a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/keygen\"><code>&lt;keygen&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a>, <a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/object\"><code>&lt;object&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a>, <a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/HTML/Element/Output\"><code>&lt;output&gt;</code></a>, <a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/HTML/Element/select\"><code>&lt;select&gt;</code></a>&nbsp;e&nbsp;<a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/HTML/Element/textarea\"><code>&lt;textarea&gt;</code></a>.</dd>\n <dt id=\"labelable\"><a name=\"Form_labelable\">labelable</a></dt>\n <dd>Elementos que podem ser associados com elementos&nbsp;<a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/HTML/Element/label\"><code>&lt;label&gt;</code></a>. Contém&nbsp;<a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/HTML/Element/button\"><code>&lt;button&gt;</code></a>, <a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/HTML/Element/Input\"><code>&lt;input&gt;</code></a>, <a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/keygen\"><code>&lt;keygen&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a>, <a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/HTML/Element/meter\"><code>&lt;meter&gt;</code></a>, <a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/HTML/Element/Output\"><code>&lt;output&gt;</code></a>, <a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/HTML/Element/progress\"><code>&lt;progress&gt;</code></a>, <a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/HTML/Element/select\"><code>&lt;select&gt;</code></a>&nbsp;e&nbsp;<a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/HTML/Element/textarea\"><code>&lt;textarea&gt;</code></a>.</dd>\n <dt id=\"submittable\"><a name=\"Form_submittable\">submittable</a></dt>\n <dd>Elementos que podem ser usados para construir o formulário de dados quando o formulário é enviado. Contém&nbsp;<a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/HTML/Element/button\"><code>&lt;button&gt;</code></a>, <a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/HTML/Element/Input\"><code>&lt;input&gt;</code></a>, <a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/keygen\"><code>&lt;keygen&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a>, <a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/object\"><code>&lt;object&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a>, <a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/HTML/Element/select\"><code>&lt;select&gt;</code></a>, e&nbsp;<a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/HTML/Element/textarea\"><code>&lt;textarea&gt;</code></a>.</dd>\n <dt id=\"resettable\"><a name=\"Form_resettable\">resettable</a></dt>\n <dd>Elementos que podem ser afetados quando um formulário é reinicializado. Contém&nbsp;<a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/HTML/Element/Input\"><code>&lt;input&gt;</code></a>, <a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/keygen\"><code>&lt;keygen&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a>, <a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/HTML/Element/Output\"><code>&lt;output&gt;</code></a>,<a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/HTML/Element/select\"><code>&lt;select&gt;</code></a>&nbsp;e&nbsp;<a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/HTML/Element/textarea\"><code>&lt;textarea&gt;</code></a>.</dd>\n</dl>","titleAsText":"Conteúdo associado ao form"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"modelo_de_conteúdo_transparente","title":"Modelo de conteúdo transparente","isH3":false,"content":"<p>Se um elemento tem um modelo de conteúdo transparente, então seu&nbsp;conteúdo&nbsp;deve&nbsp;ser estruturado de tal forma que ele seja um HTML5 válido, mesmo se o elemento transparente for removido e substituído pelos elementos filhos.</p>\n\n<p>Por exemplo, os elementos&nbsp;<a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/HTML/Element/del\"><code>&lt;del&gt;</code></a> e&nbsp;<a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/HTML/Element/ins\"><code>&lt;ins&gt;</code></a> são transparentes:</p>\n\n<pre class=\"notranslate\">&lt;p&gt;We hold these truths to be &lt;del&gt;&lt;em&gt;sacred &amp;amp; undeniable&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/del&gt; &lt;ins&gt;self-evident&lt;/ins&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;\n</pre>\n\n<p>Se aqueles elementos forem removidos, esse fragmento continuaria sendo um HTML válido.</p>\n\n<pre class=\"notranslate\">&lt;p&gt;We hold these truths to be &lt;em&gt;sacred &amp;amp; undeniable&lt;/em&gt; self-evident.&lt;/p&gt;\n</pre>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"outros_modelos_de_conteúdo","title":"Outros modelos de conteúdo","isH3":false,"content":"<p>Raiz de secionamento.</p>"}}],"toc":[{"text":"Principais categorias de conteúdo","id":"principais_categorias_de_conteúdo"},{"text":"Modelo de conteúdo transparente","id":"modelo_de_conteúdo_transparente"},{"text":"Outros modelos de conteúdo","id":"outros_modelos_de_conteúdo"}],"summary":"Cada elemento HTML deve permanecer, por regras, definindo que tipo de conteúdo ele pode ter. Essas regras estão agrupadas em modelos de conteúdo para muitos elementos. Cada elemento HTML pertence a nenhum, um, ou múltiplos modelos de conteúdo, cada regra de definição que o conteúdo do elemento deve seguir em um documento HTML.","popularity":0.0003,"modified":"2022-07-19T02:29:32.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"Inhaltskategorien","locale":"de","native":"Deutsch"},{"title":"Content categories","locale":"en-US","native":"English (US)"},{"title":"Categorías de contenido","locale":"es","native":"Español"},{"title":"Catégories de contenu","locale":"fr","native":"Français"},{"title":"コンテンツカテゴリー","locale":"ja","native":"日本語"},{"title":"콘텐츠 카테고리","locale":"ko","native":"한국어"},{"title":"Категории контента","locale":"ru","native":"Русский"},{"title":"内容分类","locale":"zh-CN","native":"中文 (简体)"},{"title":"內容類型","locale":"zh-TW","native":"正體中文 (繁體)"}],"source":{"folder":"pt-br/web/guide/html/content_categories","github_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/blob/main/files/pt-br/web/guide/html/content_categories/index.html","last_commit_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/commit/5fe4ab11259b37914fab41914e84897fea47d143","filename":"index.html"},"parents":[{"uri":"/pt-BR/docs/Web","title":"Tecnologia Web para desenvolvedores"},{"uri":"/pt-BR/docs/Web/Guide","title":"Guia do desenvolvedor web"},{"uri":"/pt-BR/docs/Web/Guide/HTML/Content_categories","title":"Categorias de conteúdo"}],"pageTitle":"Categorias de conteúdo - Guia do desenvolvedor web | MDN","noIndexing":false}}